                    <h2 class="u-align-center-sm u-align-center-xs u-text u-text-1">About Us</h2>
                    <p class="u-align-center-sm u-align-center-xs u-text u-text-font u-text-2"> Park N Fly is the first of its kind and only service in the Philippines wherein customers can leave their vehicles on a daily, weekly or monthly basis either for short-term or long-term parking at very reasonable rates.The building is newly constructed and state-of-the-art with multi-level parking facilities capable of accommodating approximately 200 cars. The facilities are specifically designed for air travelers in order to ensure comfortable hassle-free and worry-free travel. It is ideally located at MIA Domestic road just 500 meters from the domestic airport terminal. The indoor parking facilities are covered and provided with professional security and electronic surveillance.The company is open 24 hours a day, 365 days a year, Sundays and holidays included. The company has a comfortable lounge where customers are able to wait for their flight or while their cars undergo repairs and/or cleaning. Our concept has been developed for air travelers who wish to leave their cars safely attended while a fleet of complimentary air-conditioned shuttle vans transport them to the airport and back. In the interim, our experienced mechanics equipped with the most comprehensive diagnostic systems and specialized automotive equipments are available to service vehicles bumper to bumper, including detailing and cleaning packages such as interior shampoo and seat cover installation/removal.All amenities a motorist/traveler would ask for such as banking facilities, the largest Foodmart convenience store in the Philippines, gourmet coffee and barbershop are also available.</p>
